  Welcome to Week 4

Welcome to Week 4

Over the last few weeks, we've covered pre-production, creative direction, pitching, and cinematography. However, this week we will take things to the next level and talk about VFX.

The goal of this week is for you to have a few advanced VFX techniques under your belt for taking your projects to the next level.

This Week You'll Learn:

  • Frame Blending
  • Isolated Object Animation
  • The Puppet Tool
  • Prompt-to-Video Workflows and Enhancement
  • Compositing Green Screen Elements
  • Advanced Face Compositing
  • Looping Animations for Lifelike Scenes
  • Advanced Color Compositing

By the end of this week, you'll be equipped to create beautiful VFX shots that showcase the creative potential of AI filmmaking. I hope you learn a ton this week. I can't believe the course is almost over.
